						               													<description>This game represent land-ship voyage in the science fiction animate cartoon series 'Xabungle'.&amp;#10;This game was designed for the beginner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player goes to the destination by his land-ship. It gets the blue-stones during the voyage by the battle and the trade. Also get the blue-stones by arriving at the destination early. The player who got most minerals does a victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A rule is divided into two steps of the basic game and the advanced game, and it uses a different game board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A basic game proceeds through the straight road decided by a course, and does a battle in accordance with the indication of map.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A hex map with the geographical features is used with an advanced game. It can trade and refueling by the specific terrain. It becomes a battle when it approaches the ship of other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A battle is resolved by the card play in both rules.&amp;#10;There are the Walker machine cards, a pilot card and a weapon card in the card. A six side die is used with the total strength of each cards and the combat result table, and a battle is resolved.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
